WEBVTT

00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:02.831
Tere tulemast viimasesse õpetusse!

00:00:02.831 --> 00:00:03.288
Veendume,

00:00:03.288 --> 00:00:06.034
et kettaruum enam kunagi otsa ei

00:00:06.034 --> 00:00:06.492
saaks.

00:00:06.492 --> 00:00:08.322
Kasvatame täis repository't online,

00:00:08.322 --> 00:00:11.068
anname kustutatud ruumi tagasi poolile ja

00:00:11.068 --> 00:00:13.356
õpetame masinal mõlemat automaatselt tegema.

00:00:14.130 --> 00:00:15.706
Nii see toimib.

00:00:15.706 --> 00:00:18.332
Iga repository on fail ühises

00:00:18.332 --> 00:00:19.382
datastore poolis.

00:00:19.382 --> 00:00:21.483
Repository'd saavad kasvada online,

00:00:21.483 --> 00:00:23.058
kuni containers töötavad.

00:00:23.058 --> 00:00:25.684
Kuid andmete kustutamine repository sees

00:00:25.684 --> 00:00:27.785
ei vabasta iseenesest midagi.

00:00:27.785 --> 00:00:29.361
Trim on see,

00:00:29.361 --> 00:00:31.987
mis annab plokid tagasi poolile.

00:00:31.987 --> 00:00:34.088
Ja poliitika automatiseerib mõlemat.

00:00:37.352 --> 00:00:39.925
Fill the repository most of the way

00:00:39.925 --> 00:00:40.660
and check:

00:00:40.660 --> 00:00:42.498
the filesystem is getting tight.

00:00:48.126 --> 00:00:49.262
Peaaegu täis.

00:00:49.262 --> 00:00:50.399
Aeg kasvada.

00:00:53.677 --> 00:00:54.943
Grow it online.

00:00:54.943 --> 00:00:57.474
The encrypted container and the filesystem

00:00:57.474 --> 00:01:00.005
expand while the containers keep running

00:01:00.005 --> 00:01:01.271
— zero downtime,

00:01:01.271 --> 00:01:02.115
zero unmount.

00:01:05.115 --> 00:01:06.368
Neli gigabaiti nüüd.

00:01:06.368 --> 00:01:07.622
Midagi ei taaskäivitunud.

00:01:10.918 --> 00:01:12.162
Verify from inside:

00:01:12.162 --> 00:01:12.991
same volume,

00:01:12.991 --> 00:01:14.236
double the room.

00:01:18.848 --> 00:01:20.075
Rakendus ei märganud midagi.

00:01:23.365 --> 00:01:24.851
Now the other direction.

00:01:24.851 --> 00:01:27.452
Delete the big file — but watch:

00:01:27.452 --> 00:01:30.052
the pool does not get the space

00:01:30.052 --> 00:01:30.795
back yet.

00:01:30.795 --> 00:01:33.396
Deleted blocks stay reserved inside the image.

00:01:35.146 --> 00:01:36.221
Vabastatud repo sees,

00:01:36.221 --> 00:01:37.654
kuid ikka pildi omanduses.

00:01:40.989 --> 00:01:43.538
Trim hands those blocks back to the

00:01:43.538 --> 00:01:44.267
datastore pool,

00:01:44.267 --> 00:01:44.631
online.

00:01:44.631 --> 00:01:47.180
This is the step most setups forget.

00:01:50.180 --> 00:01:50.990
Tagasi saadud.

00:01:50.990 --> 00:01:52.609
Pool saab jälle hingata.

00:01:55.927 --> 00:01:58.552
Now stop doing this by hand.

00:01:58.552 --> 00:02:01.178
The policy enables automatic growth up

00:02:01.178 --> 00:02:03.365
to a ceiling you choose,

00:02:03.365 --> 00:02:04.678
plus scheduled trims.

00:02:09.744 --> 00:02:10.641
Poliitika salvestatud.

00:02:10.641 --> 00:02:12.434
Masin võtab siit üle.

00:02:15.697 --> 00:02:16.740
Read it back:

00:02:16.740 --> 00:02:17.435
auto-grow on,

00:02:17.435 --> 00:02:18.826
ceiling at eight gigabytes,

00:02:18.826 --> 00:02:20.216
trim on a schedule.

00:02:24.834 --> 00:02:25.774
Seadistatud korra,

00:02:25.774 --> 00:02:26.715
unustatud turvaliselt.

00:02:30.011 --> 00:02:32.802
And the view that ties it together:

00:02:32.802 --> 00:02:35.193
storage health shows every repo's usage,

00:02:35.193 --> 00:02:35.991
the pool,

00:02:35.991 --> 00:02:38.781
and how much copy-on-write sharing is saving

00:02:38.781 --> 00:02:39.180
you.

00:02:39.180 --> 00:02:40.217
Üks vaade:

00:02:40.217 --> 00:02:40.736
kasutus,

00:02:40.736 --> 00:02:42.811
kokkuhoid ja ruumi kasvuks.

00:02:43.589 --> 00:02:45.979
Ja sellega on sari läbi!

00:02:45.979 --> 00:02:46.935
Kaheksateist õpetust,

00:02:46.935 --> 00:02:48.847
installimisest kuni automaatse salvestushalduseni.

00:02:48.847 --> 00:02:51.716
Sinu serverid on jälle sinu omad.

00:02:51.716 --> 00:02:53.150
Aitäh vaatamise eest!
